summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5866 for the improvement of West Genesee Street, from 21st Avenue Southwest to 23rd Avenue Southwest; and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues; by constructing concrete sidewalks and concrete stairway and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 77282, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
